<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.7.8">
<l>pantār viralāḷ pāñcāli kūntal muṭikkap pāratattu</l>
<l>kantār kaḷiṟṟuk kaḻalmaṉṉar kalaṅkac caṅkam vāyvaittāṉ</l>
<l>centā maraimē layaṉōṭu civaṉu maṉaiya perumaiyōr</l>
<l>nantā vaṇkai maṟaiyōrvāḻ naṟaiyūr niṉṟa nampiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who placed at his lips the conch so that kings with [war] anklets</l>
<l rend="indent">on elephants with the odor [of musth] were terrified</l>
<l>In the Bhārata [War], so Pāñcāli, she with string-filled fingers,</l>
<l rend="indent">could tie up her hair [again],</l>
<l>Is the noble who stands in Naṟaiyūr where dwell Vedic experts</l>
<l rend="indent">with hands of unending bounty,</l>
<l>Great ones who resemble Śiva and Unborn [Brahmā] on the rosy lotus.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
